r />\n好在而家用煤氣冇問題"},{"pid":"db07628689870cc01e0e0f98282a63750b554cca","tid":18734,"uid":20989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冬天既然要同個爐鬥快，點解唔用水煲煲水倒落水筒/盤沖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 變通下啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細細個我都係俾老豆老母咁沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好在而家用煤氣冇問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我細個都係 但大個左 大家都忙 時間又唔夾<br />\n煲一兜比一個人沖其實好浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b474f8fd036795e2252ced7ea129267daf8b4f98","tid":18734,"uid":38959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T17:35:24.000Z","msg":"一分鐘極速沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca0f0be779cf46a22f1862000482fce5b540f01","tid":18734,"uid":29708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:00:08.000Z","msg":"依家嘅氣溫還可以 到一二月夜晚得個幾度 好啲有十一二度 大容量照樣要扭細個熱水先沖到15分鐘以上<br />\n<br />\n利申20年德國寶儲水式電熱水爐用家"},{"pid":"e7f3f3000c706a117dd9ce9e5e650c8849875cd5","tid":18734,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T03:02:05.000Z","msg":"呢幾日都暖左"},{"pid":"0c17fcdd61039324769f2505b8b70156ef14921c","tid":18734,"uid":34838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:38:26.000Z","msg":"由煤氣爐換做儲水式熱水爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e842ca851017ac131bb96dfe2f2b67271fa5612b","tid":18734,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e8c2a72a2cc1c811ae60d37246ea99b20785e7","tid":18734,"uid":16404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:45:20.000Z","msg":"電熱水爐 我細細個就開始用架啦<img s